5
One Move Captures Black (18)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj White makes the endgame play at 1. When black blocks at 2, should white connects at \b\f1 A\b0\f0 ?
\par \pard
\par In fact, there is a move white can play to capture black. Please find the move.
\par
\par
\par }
