Diagram 2 (Impossible)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It does not work for white to directly attack black at 1 either. Of course black plays dansu with 2 and up to 4, black lives.
\par
\par White has merely given black some stones as a present.
\par
\par There ia move to capture black. Please think carefully and then look at the next diagram.
\par }
